OL,3,CCollege lecturer union votes to reject
OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,FMembers of a trade union representing
OL,7,Flecturers at further education
OL,8,Fcolleges in Northern Ireland have
OL,9,Fvoted to reject a pay offer.
OL,11,FThe lecturers were offered a 5%
OL,12,Fincrease as well as an unconsolidated
OL,13,Fpayment of #1,500.
OL,15,FIt comes after industrial action over
OL,16,Fpay.
OL,18,FMembers of the NASUWT voted against
OL,19,Faccepting it.
