OL,3,CCollege lecturer union votes to reject
OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,FThe union said 87% of the members
OL,7,Fvoted in favour of rejecting the
OL,8,Foffer, with a turnout of 63%.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, the union said that 71% of
OL,11,Fmembers said they were prepared to
OL,12,Ftake further strike action, and 93%
OL,13,Fsaid they were prepared to take
OL,14,Ffurther action short of strike action.
OL,16,FThe NASUWT said its National Action
OL,17,FCommittee will consider the results of
OL,18,Fthe member survey before deciding on
OL,19,Fthe union's next steps.
