OL,3,CCollege lecturer union votes to reject
OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,FDr Patrick Roach, NASUWT general
OL,7,Fsecretary, urged the Stormont Economy
OL,8,FMinister Conor Murphy to urgently
OL,9,Fengage with the union.
OL,11,F"Northern Ireland's further education
OL,12,Flecturers are fed up with being
OL,13,Ftreated as second class teachers by
OL,14,Fsuccessive ministers for the economy
OL,15,Fand the college employers," he said.
OL,17,F"NASUWT further education lecturers
OL,18,Fhave sent a clear signal that they are
OL,19,Fnot prepared to let the pay gap widen
OL,20,Fwith teachers in schools.
