OL,6,F"The minister for the economy must now
OL,7,Furgently engage with the NASUWT to
OL,8,Fdevelop a plan which will close the
OL,9,Fpay gap in education in Northern
OL,10,FIreland."
OL,12,FMaxine Murphy-Higgins, NASUWT Northern
OL,13,FIreland policy casework official,
OL,14,Fadded: "For too long, further
OL,15,Feducation lecturers have watched the
OL,16,Fpay gap widen. They are now faced with
OL,17,Fa situation where the gap will widen
OL,18,Ffurther. The union is not surprised
OL,19,Fthat members have voted to reject this
OL,20,Foffer.
