OL,3,CCollege lecturer union votes to reject
OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,F"The current pay situation in further
OL,7,Feducation is a shambles which reflects
OL,8,Fthe dysfunctional situation on the
OL,9,Flecturers' negotiating committee where
OL,10,Fthe employers seem unable to work with
OL,11,Feach other never mind the trade
OL,12,Funions".
OL,14,F"It is now incumbent on the minister
OL,15,Fto fix the negotiating arrangements,
OL,16,Fstop the redundancy process, increase
OL,17,Fpay and ensure that lecturers have
OL,18,Fworking conditions which are
OL,19,Fstatutorily compliant and capable of
OL,20,Fenticing new lecturers into the
OL,21,Fcolleges."
