OL,6,FSpeaking in the Stormont Assembly on
OL,7,FTuesday during questions for his
OL,8,Fdepartment, Mr Murphy said he hoped
OL,9,Fthe trade unions would take up the pay
OL,10,Foffer.
OL,12,F"What we're trying to do with the
OL,13,Famount of money available today is
OL,14,Ftrying to get a settlement for this
OL,15,Fyear to try and give people some
OL,16,Fsupport and agree together to set that
OL,17,Ftrajectory for future years in terms
OL,18,Fof aligning that with with teachers,"
OL,19,Fhe said.
